

Dev Server
**De-activate all security plugins**
1) tar -czvf wp-content.tar.gz wp-content -> download
2) push latest theme to github
3) phmyadmin -> export database (make sure create if not exists is NOT checked)
4) download wp-config.php & .htaccess
5) Change url in database

Live Server (phpMyAdmin)
1) backup database
2) Make new databse on CPANEL (post 2080)
3) Make new user for database
4) Import Database

Live Server (FTP)
1) push up new wp_content to the ftp folder
2) make a copy of wp_content
3) decompress it to the wp_content folder
4) Edit the wp-config.php file to point to the right database
5) Open the 'options' table and update the url.
6)





